<div class="intro">
    <h2>Who is Joel Hilton?</h2>
    <p>Joel Hilton is a film critic with a deep background in Film Studies from BYU, and he brings his expertise to his work as a movie reviewer for ClearPlay 
        and the host of the Baconsale podcast. With a keen eye for quality, Joel curates a growing movie collection of 
        only the most worthy films, tracking them meticulously in a personalized system.</p>
</div>


<div class="Baconsale">
    <h2>Baconsale</h2>
    <p>Joel Hilton is a passionate film enthusiast who brings his expertise and humor to Baconsale, a family-friendly pop culture podcast where he and his co-hosts 
        dive into movies, music, TV, food, video games, and more. With a background in Film Studies from BYU and experience as a movie reviewer for ClearPlay, 
        Joel offers insightful commentary, witty debates, and deep-cut film knowledge that elevate each episode. Whether he's analyzing blockbuster hits, uncovering 
        hidden gems, or playfully sparring with his co-hosts, Joel's love for cinema and pop culture shines through, making Baconsale an entertaining and engaging experience for listeners.</p>
   
