<div class="QuickWits">
    <h2>Quick Wits Comedy</h2>
    <p>Joel Hilton is a key member of Quick Wits, an improvisational comedy troupe that brings fast-paced, audience-driven comedy to Utah. 
        With his sharp wit and years of experience, Joel helps transform spontaneous audience suggestions into hilarious, unscripted performances. 
        Quick Wits is known for its high-energy shows, reminiscent of Whose Line Is It Anyway?, where anything can happen and no two performances 
        are ever the same. Whether you're looking for clever wordplay, outrageous characters, or quick-thinking humor, Joel and the Quick Wits team 
        guarantee a night full of laughter.</p>
